  ('disabled-0a2fc18c-moex-00259', 'disabled-0a2fc18c', 'disabled-0a2fc18c-moex-110-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-disabled-0a2fc18c-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '消費者的vonNeumann-Morgenstern效用函數為U(y)=ln(y)，其中y為所得 而ln(.)自然對數函數。此效用函數的Arrow-Pratt 絕對風險趨避指標值為何？', '["0", "1", "1/y", "-1/y2"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:38:26+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2d98a20a2928", "answer_pdf_sha1": "0f20895e9ec9", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110050", "c": "305", "s": "0906", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 10, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "disabled", "civil_category": "經建行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('disabled-0a2fc18c-moex-00260', 'disabled-0a2fc18c', 'disabled-0a2fc18c-moex-110-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-disabled-0a2fc18c-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '如果我們無法在不損及他人福利的情況下同時增加某些人的福利，則此稱為：', '["柏拉圖最適", "第一福利定理", "第二福利定理", "柏拉圖改善"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:38:26+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2d98a20a2928", "answer_pdf_sha1": "0f20895e9ec9", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110050", "c": "305", "s": "0906", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 11, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "disabled", "civil_category": "經建行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('disabled-0a2fc18c-moex-00261', 'disabled-0a2fc18c', 'disabled-0a2fc18c-moex-110-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-disabled-0a2fc18c-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '廠商生產過程，排放污水至河流：', '["因為私人成本小於社會成本，造成市場機能自由決定下之產量小於社會福 利最大產量", "因為私人成本小於社會成本，造成市場機能自由決定下之產量大於社會福 利最大產量", "因為私人成本大於社會成本，造成市場機能自由決定下之產量小於社會福 利最大產量", "因為私人成本大於社會成本，造成市場機能自由決定下之產量大於社會福 利最大產量"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:38:26+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2d98a20a2928", "answer_pdf_sha1": "0f20895e9ec9", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110050", "c": "305", "s": "0906", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 12, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "disabled", "civil_category": "經建行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('disabled-0a2fc18c-moex-00262', 'disabled-0a2fc18c', 'disabled-0a2fc18c-moex-110-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-disabled-0a2fc18c-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者會使得可貸資金市場之均衡利率上升，且均衡可貸資金數量下降？', '["政府預算赤字增加", "投資抵減法案鼓勵投資", "稅法改革鼓勵儲蓄", "企業對於獲利前景變得較為樂觀"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:38:26+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2d98a20a2928", "answer_pdf_sha1": "0f20895e9ec9", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110050", "c": "305", "s": "0906", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 13, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "disabled", "civil_category": "經建行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
